StatsRows

public StatsRows(String shortName,
                 String name,
                 Scape iteratingScape,
                 Collection<StatsPredicateRow<T>> rows,
                 String columnHeading,
                 StatsFunction<T> function,
                 double ratioMultiplier)
Construct from a collection of StatsPredicateRows that collects the same value for each row (but with a different predicate) per iteration and produces an average percentage over all iterations. The percentage denominator is specified by the StatsPredicateRow denominator. Each StatsPredicateRow acts on a subset of the scape, as determined by its StatsPredicate.

Type Parameters:
T - type of scape members
Parameters:
shortName - short name
name - name
iteratingScape - scape. Used by CollectorFunctionPerIteration to get the current iteration. If null then will use CollectorFunction instead.
rows - rows to create in the table
columnHeading - column heading
function - value to collect from simulation.
ratioMultiplier - amount to multiple the ratio by (eg: 100 to get percentage)

Construct from a collection of StatsFunctionRows with the default ratio multiplier.

Type Parameters:

name - name
iteratingScape - scape. Used by CollectorFunctionPerIteration to get the current iteration. If null then will use CollectorFunction instead.
rows - rows to create in the table

StatsRows

public StatsRows(String shortName,
                 String name,
                 Scape iteratingScape,
                 Collection<StatsFunctionRow<T>> rows,
                 String columnHeading,
                 StatsPredicate<T> predicate,
                 double ratioMultiplier)
Construct from a collection of StatsFunctionRows that collects a different value for each row, but with the same predicate, per iteration and produces an average ratio over all iterations. The ratio denominator is specified by the StatsFunctionRow denominator. Each StatsFunctionRow acts on a subset of the scape, as determined by its StatsPredicate.

Type Parameters:
T - type of scape members
Parameters:
shortName - short name
name - name
iteratingScape - scape. Used by CollectorFunctionPerIteration to get the current iteration. If null then will use CollectorFunction instead.
rows - rows to create in the table
columnHeading - column heading
predicate - predicate to apply to all rows. If null, collects data for all members.
ratioMultiplier - amount to multiple the ratio by (eg: 100 to get percentage)
